Subject: [PATCH 0480/1074] MLK-9640-2: ARM: dts: imx6sx: add ldo-bypass
 support

add ldo-bypass support for all mx6sx board. The default mode
is ldo-bypass  mode, you can choose ldo-enable mode by use
*-ldo.dtb

Signed-off-by: Robin Gong <b38343@freescale.com>
[Original patch taken from git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git]
Signed-off-by: Biyao Zhai <biyao.zhai@windriver.com>
